---
title: Hey, Honey! Salmon with Roasted Broccoli & Zesty Green Beans
description: Fishing for a fresh, sea-faring meal? We’ve got just the thing. Here, spice-rubbed salmon fillets are seared until crisp-skinned and flaky, then drizzled with a lemony, buttery honey Dijon sauce. Paired with tender roasted potato wedges and zesty green beans, it’s a meal that’s as elegant as it is delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63da94108c8a1a731809ffee-95c14323.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/hey-honey-salmon-63da94108c8a1a731809ffee-014e0969.pdf
